# (fsnotify THIS — Axis 17 expands to 2 variants) → expected
# R655 TS-Node=71 → R656 96th language.  This is the 2nd of 3
# leader bumps in the current segment.
#
# This completion EXPANDS Axis 17 (FILE WATCHING) to TWO documented
# variants — symmetrically distributed across Rust (notify R653)
# and Go (fsnotify THIS R654).  TS-Node Axis 17 variant expected
# in R655 (likely chokidar by Paul Miller) to complete three-
